Hasaacas       awd RTU                    [awarded 3-0]
  [Hasaacas showed in deep green jerseys, RTU in light green; the
   referee considered this a colour clash and awarded the match to
   Hasaacas after 35 minutes; however, RTU claim to have shown in 
   their blue home jerseys after 25 minutes of discussions and 
   originally protested the award successfully, a replay being
   scheduled for Jan 31 but not played following an appeal by Hasaacas
   who eventually were awarded the match 3-0 on Mar 5]

